results.name: Number of isomorphism classes of associative closed binary operations (semigroups) on a set of order n, listed by class size.
comment: Elements per row: 1,2,4,8,16,30,... (given by A027423, number of positive divisors of n!)
A023814(x) is equal to the sum of the products of each element in row x of this sequence and the corresponding element of A079210.
The sum of each row n is given by A027851(n).
link: C. van den Bosch, Closed binary operations on small sets
Index entries for sequences related to semigroups
